PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS (TUKTUT NOGAIT NATIONAL PARK, NORTHWEST TERRITORIES AND NUNAVUT) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of land in the Northwest Territories and Nunavut until March 1, 2008, and (b) the repeal of a similar Order made in 1998.
